reviews.review_text:
no rating phil sounds very nice here -- he had an amazing tone in these years that really is a revelation -- it took 20 years to sound like this -- from taking a stereo speaker and a 250 watt amp to playing CLEAR NOTE PERFECT six string melodic bass in a 20,000 seat arena, and every seat can hear the pick slide off the string...


pick it up at the top of the playing jam, for a 30 second LESH LESSON
